# VastraCo — Complete Project Documentation

VastraCo is a cloud-native fashion e-commerce platform built as a microservices application. It includes an AI-powered shopping assistant, a full GitOps CI/CD pipeline, and production infrastructure deployed on AWS EKS using Terraform, Helm, and ArgoCD.

