## 11. Environment Variables Reference

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` for local development. On EKS, all sensitive values are injected from AWS Secrets Manager via the CSI Driver; non-sensitive values come from ConfigMaps.

| Variable | Local Default | EKS Source | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `JWT_SECRET` | (set manually) | `vastraco/jwt-secret` | JWT signing secret (min 32 chars) |
| `USER_DB_HOST` | `users-db` | `vastraco/db-creds` | PostgreSQL host for user service |
| `USER_DB_PORT` | `5432` | ConfigMap | PostgreSQL port |
| `USER_DB_NAME` | `users_db` | ConfigMap | Database name for user service |
| `USER_DB_USER` | `vastraco_user` | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB username for user service |
| `USER_DB_PASSWORD` | (set manually) | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB password for user service |
| `PRODUCT_DB_HOST` | `products-db` | `vastraco/db-creds` | PostgreSQL host for product service |
| `PRODUCT_DB_PORT` | `5432` | ConfigMap | PostgreSQL port |
| `PRODUCT_DB_NAME` | `products_db` | ConfigMap | Database name for product service |
| `PRODUCT_DB_USER` | `vastraco_product` | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB username for product service |
| `PRODUCT_DB_PASSWORD` | (set manually) | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB password for product service |
| `ORDER_DB_HOST` | `orders-db` | `vastraco/db-creds` | PostgreSQL host for order service |
| `ORDER_DB_PORT` | `5432` | ConfigMap | PostgreSQL port |
| `ORDER_DB_NAME` | `orders_db` | ConfigMap | Database name for order service |
| `ORDER_DB_USER` | `vastraco_order` | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB username for order service |
| `ORDER_DB_PASSWORD` | (set manually) | `vastraco/db-creds` | DB password for order service |
| `PRODUCT_SERVICE_URL` | `http://product-service:3002` | ConfigMap | Internal URL for product service |
| `ORDER_SERVICE_URL` | `http://order-service:3003` | ConfigMap | Internal URL for order service |
| `USER_SERVICE_URL` | `http://user-service:3001` | ConfigMap | Internal URL for user service |
| `GROQ_API_KEY` | (set manually) | `vastraco/app-secrets` | Groq API key (from console.groq.com) |
| `GROQ_MODEL` | `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` | ConfigMap | Groq model ID |

**Recommended Groq Models:**

| Model | Context | Use Case |
|---|---|---|
| `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` | 131k tokens | Production (recommended) |
| `llama-3.1-8b-instant` | 128k tokens | Low latency / cost optimization |
| `meta-llama/llama-4-scout-17b-16e-instruct` | 10k tokens | Newest Meta model |

